net.minecraftforge.fml.event.lifecycle

Class InterModEnqueueEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraftforge.eventbus.api.Event
      • net.minecraftforge.fml.event.lifecycle.ModLifecycleEvent
        • net.minecraftforge.fml.event.lifecycle.InterModEnqueueEvent

  • public class InterModEnqueueEvent
extends ModLifecycleEvent
    This is the third of four commonly called events during mod lifecycle startup. Called before InterModProcessEvent Called after FMLClientSetupEvent or FMLDedicatedServerSetupEvent Enqueue InterModComms messages to other mods with this event. This is a parallel dispatch event.
